<Content>Absolutely Fabulous! My trip to Barcelona was a birthday present for my partner and this hotel helped to make it a truely special one. From the moment we arrived until the moment we checked out the staff were friendly, efficient, and went out of their way to assist us in anyway they could. We stayed in a standard double room (a description that doesn't do it any justice) - Our room was tastefully decorated and spacious (as was the bathroom); equipped with a flat screen television and extra comfy bed, we found it hard to get up in the morning! Our room was street facing but the windows effectively blocked out the noise of passing traffic.The hotel is in a great location. Surrounded by plenty of cafes, restaurants and designer outlets, the hotel is 5-10 minutes away from the metro station Diagonal by foot; a train station is around the corner; and La Rambla is within walking distance (10-15 minutes).Our time at the hotel was worth every penny and we will definitely be staying there again when we next visit Barcelona. We recommend this hotel to any traveller looking for some luxury at reasonable prices. 
